#- Day 1.
One day a Man named dane Knew a good Tree named Jimmy But one day He got VICIOUS, And pulled out an Axe and Shears and Slowly he Choped bark by bark off of jimmy then leaf by leaf. Then a man Named 4801 Tried to stop this evil Villian but It was no
#- use so He pulled out a sapling of another tree he MURDERED. and Bonemealed as quick as possiable. He knew the Tree guardian Leafy would be on to kill him so to Cover up the sence of the crime he Truned jimmy into a CARPET AND A FLOOR.
GOD IS WATCHING Q.Q
